Hilda Simms https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hilda_Simms 0 Hilda Simms (born Hilda Moses, April 15, 1918 – February 6, 1994) was an African-American stage actress, best known for her starring role on Broadway in Anna Lucasta.
